-Contact 
-Alternate contact 
- Charts --> no of beds available / total no of beds 
- Charts --> no of opds available / total no of opds 
- Charts --> no of icus available / total no of icus 
- Charts --> no of general ward available / total no of general ward 
- Charts --> no of shared room available / total no of shared room 

















